{"tid":919854,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONEPIECE 海賊王 926 情報","createTime":"2018-11-28T11:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T05:44:25.000Z","uid":130563,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7a17315a9caad26bab5537669fadc573e3be4ac9","tid":919854,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"街上的瓦版上。<br />\n有很多像是武士的人 有旭日模樣 光月家的標誌。<br />\n是光月家回來了嗎？<br />\n娜美與女忍者潛入了某地。<br />\n<br />\n路飛與基德在搬運石頭。<br />\n明明還銬著海樓石但卻搬運了很多。<br />\n兩人爭先恐後吃飯。<br />\n河馬的看守非常生氣。<br />\n作為懲罰，他將兩個人都扔到了河馬的口中。<br />\n但不知為何河馬卻倒下了。<br />\n路飛與基德從河馬嘴裡出來。<br />\n路飛手上還抱著一個孩子。<br />\n梆梆！（三味線擬聲詞）"},{"pid":"89fef082c61356299055a363430170de7f56c1da","tid":919854,"uid":130563,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"一講路飛個劇情就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8824e809f610a7edeb7cc1922bcc1586fd54b6b4","tid":919854,"uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":32,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"尾田幾時死"},{"pid":"dd42e9e2e2d8e04e2d0b91bd13b00d07583d483f","tid":919854,"uid":147489,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"爭食飯 用一畫畫<br />\n食飯 又用一頁畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490668f96ac06105cdf434f5a78ba04fc84b093f","tid":919854,"uid":70794,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8824e809f610a7edeb7cc1922bcc1586fd54b6b4","tid":919854,"uid":213877,"like":9,"dislike":32,"score":-23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"尾田幾時死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"咪撚講廢話啦 屌"},{"pid":"57ad13a43314dbc799a16aad4461bd90449e9a61","tid":919854,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"490668f96ac06105cdf434f5a78ba04fc84b093f","tid":919854,"uid":70794,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8824e809f610a7edeb7cc19